551
00:44:34.672 --> 00:44:36.935
We're almost there. baby.
We're almost home.

552
00:44:38.240 --> 00:44:40.939
Holy sh...

553
00:44:45.378 --> 00:44:46.814
Captain?

554
00:44:46.988 --> 00:44:49.817
Okay. baby. we're home.
We're home.

555
00:44:51.123 --> 00:44:54.126
