573
00:45:47.701 --> 00:45:49.007
Here.

574
00:46:17.470 --> 00:46:21.822
Confirming the target address.
624 Spring Drive.

575
00:46:21.996 --> 00:46:23.563
Copy that.
We're eight minutes out.

576
00:46:23.737 --> 00:46:26.871
