654
00:52:51.733 --> 00:52:53.170
Send six ambulances.

655
00:52:54.475 --> 00:52:55.607
Nikki.

656
00:52:56.912 --> 00:52:58.871
Nikki Halsted.

657
00:53:08.054 --> 00:53:09.925
